data.description: Fantastic 3BR (all on one level) end-unit in Chanhassen's heart that is close to shops, dining, lakes, parks, and major roads. This location is so hard to beat! 3 minutes to Lifetime and about 5 minutes to the new Costco in Chaska. Great efficient layout with large windows for so much natural light, living room with a toasty gas fireplace, eat in kitchen, private side patio, spacious vaulted primary bedroom with a large walk in closet & walk through bath. Updates that were done over the very recent years: engineered hardwood flooring, kitchen tile, newer cabinet hardware, light fixtures, newer carpet.  2 or 3 years old kitchen sink osmosis system, 2020 water heater, 2023 water softener,  new garbage disposal.  New roof in 2021 and a fairly roomy 2-car attached garage.  Don't miss this one!
